items.title: A better way of thinking about the AI bubble
items.description: AI isn't all or nothing, and even good bets can turn sour if you aren't careful about how you make them.

items.title: Rad Power Bikes faces shutdown in January without new funding
items.description: The company is "still fighting to find ways to continue" according to an email viewed by TechCrunch.

items.title: Kaltura acquires eSelf, founded by creator of Snap’s AI, in $27M deal
items.description: Kaltura acquires AI avatar startup eSelf to integrate generative AI into enterprise video and learning tools.

items.title: Google brings Gemini to the Google TV Streamer
items.description: The tech giant says the change will enable users to use their voice more naturally to access content and more.

items.title: AI PowerPoint-killer Gamma hits $2.1B valuation, $100M ARR, founder says
items.description: Gamma is growing quickly, and profitably, its co-founder CEO Grant Lee says.
